title: Celtic's Rodgers 'delighted' by Gerrard's move into management
text:
Celtic's Rodgers 'delighted' by Gerrard's move into management 1:55pm EDT - 01:26
Celtic manager Brendan Rodgers says he is 'delighted' for 'ultra-professional' Steven Gerrard, who takes over at the club's chief rivals Rangers.
